      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"rest\" feels like such a joke right now. like, i can sleep for ten hours and i'll still wake up feeling this heavy, this hollow. it's not just being sleepy, it's like my soul is just... exhausted. everything feels so heavy and meaningless. even the thought of trying to \"reach out\" or \"fix it\" feels like more work that i just don't have the energy for. i just want a way to actually stop feeling this way. a real way to make the weight go away.",
